   Trading Halt
   Braked Steep
   Stock Slide
   ----
   By George Anders and Jeff Bailey
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C1
</SO>
